Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,基於天命將汝之羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,剝奪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:57.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:00:59.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,beast有了死亡概念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,羅瑪尼 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,藤丸 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,現在的話就能完全消滅beast
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:11.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,大家 一起進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:15.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,好 我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:31.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:34.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,瑪修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,冥界的赤雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.36,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:23.82,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,難 難道她打算回到地面？
